pageProduct.name: Andalou Age Defying Deep Wrinkle Dermal Filler 18ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Fruit stem cell complex, resveratrol CoQ10 and goji glycopeptides boost cell energy for dermal vitality, supporting essential building blocks, collagen and elastin, as capuacu butter reduces skin tension to visibly plump and smooth fine lines and wrinkles.

Warnings

For external use only. Avoid direct contact with eyes.

Common Uses

Wrinkle Filler For Dry, Very Dry Skin Types

Ingredients

Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice*, Purified Water (Aqua), Vegetable Glycerin, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Cetyl Alcohol, Stearyl Alcohol, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter*, Glyceryl Stearate, Allantoin, Fruit Stem Cells (Malus Domestica, Solar Vitis) and BioActive Berry Complex*, Firming Complex [Hydrolyzed Myrtus Communis (Myrtle) Leaf Extract, Resveratrol, Ubiquinone (CoQ10), Lycium Barbarum (Goji) Fruit Extract], Tocopherol, Theobroma Grandiflorum (Cupuacu) Seed Butter, Sodium Hyaluronate, Magnesium Ascorbyl Phosphate (Vitamin C), Aspalathus Linearis (Rooibos) Extract*†, Hibiscus Sabdariffa Flower Extract*†, Camellia Sinensis (White Tea) Leaf Extract*†, Phenethyl Alcohol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Vanilla Isolates *Certified Organic Ingredients †Fair Trade Ingredients

Directions

AM & PM. Apply to clean skin directly on fine lines and wrinkles around eyes, mouth, cheeks, and forehead. Follow with moisturizer.
